// ░░░╚═╝░░░╚═╝░░╚═╝░░╚═╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚═════╝░╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝░╚════╝░░░░╚═╝░░░

configuration {
    show-icons:           true;
    display-drun:         "";
    display-filebrowser:  "";
    display-window:       "";
    drun-display-format:  "{name}";
    font:                 "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font 10";
}

@import "../colors.rasi"

/* Main Window Setup */
window {
    enabled:              true;
    fullscreen:           false;
    location:             center;      /* Centers the panel on screen */
    width:                90%;         /* Gives a clean floating dock appearance */
    max-width:            1400px;      /* Prevents over-stretching on ultrawide monitors */
    transparency:         "real";
    cursor:               "default";
    spacing:              0px;
    padding:              20px;
    border:               2px;
    border-color:         @primary;    /* Frame border matching your accent color */
    border-radius:        20px;        /* Smooth modern corners */
    background-color:     @surface;
}

/* Main Box Container */
mainbox {
    enabled:              true;
    children:             [ "listview" ];
    background-color:     transparent;
}

/* Wallpaper Grid Layout */
listview {
    enabled:              true;
    columns:              6;
    lines:                1;
    spacing:              20px;
    padding:              10px;
    cycle:                true;
    dynamic:              false;
    scrollbar:            false;
    layout:               vertical;
    reverse:              false;
    fixed-height:         true;
    fixed-columns:        true;
    cursor:               "default";
    background-color:     transparent;
    text-color:           @on-surface;
}

/* Individual Wallpaper Element Slot */
element {
    enabled:              true;
    orientation:          vertical;
    children:             [ "element-icon" ]; /* Only renders the icon, removing the text below */
    spacing:              0px;
    padding:              15px;
    border-radius:        16px;
    border:               2px;
    border-color:         transparent;
    cursor:               pointer;
    background-color:     transparent;
    text-color:           @on-surface;
}

/* Normal State */
element normal.normal {
    background-color:     transparent;
}

/* Selected State Style */
element selected.normal {
    background-color:     @bg-alt;     /* Subtle contrast background behind the image */
    border-color:         @primary;    /* Accent color border around the selection */
}

/* Image Thumbnail Properties */
element-icon {
    size:                 200px;
    cursor:               inherit;
    border-radius:        12px;        /* Inner rounding for the images */
    background-color:     transparent;
    text-color:           inherit;
}

/* Error Handling UI */
error-message {
    text-color:           @on-surface;
    background-color:     @surface;
    children:             [ "textbox" ];
}

textbox {
    text-color:           inherit;
    background-color:     inherit;
    vertical-align:       0.5;
    horizontal-align:     0.5;
}


